<p data-start="2403" data-end="2467">Una <strong data-start="2407" data-end="2436">interfaz web centralizada</strong> (dashboard) puede usarse para:</p>
<ul data-start="2468" data-end="2638">
<li data-start="2468" data-end="2514">
